{"id": "1518527530737467533", "channel_id": "1518527530737467533", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**V2.5.2 全新唤醒体✦庞托斯**\n\n「很好，抬起头，露出你的喉咙。再告诉我一次，你依然信奉你那肮脏的神吗？」\n「我，即此处唯一的神祇，深渊之主，庞托斯。」\n✦ 庞托斯CV：诹访部顺一\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n**V2.5.2 New Awakener✦Pontos**\n\n\"Good. Head up. Bare your throat. Now tell me once more: do you still worship that filthy god of yours?\"\n\"I am the only god of this place—Pontos, the Lord of the Great Abyss.\"\n✦ Pontos VA: Junichi Suwabe\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n**V2.5.2 신규 각성체✦폰토스**\n\n\"좋아, 고개를 들거라. 네 목을 드러내라. 다시 한 번 말해보아라, 너는 여전히 그 더러운 신을 믿고 있느냐?\"\n\"나는 곧 여기의 유일한 신이자, 심연의 주인, 폰토스다.\"\n✦ 폰토스 CV: 스와베 쥰이치", "timestamp": "2026-06-22T08:06:16.205000+00:00", "pinned": true, "thread_id": "1518527530737467533", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Leigh_wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 62}, {"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 32}, {"emoji": "Dexter_cheer", "emoji_id": "1459073619622891635", "count": 7}, {"emoji": "Leigh_love", "emoji_id": "1468258513405870121", "count": 7}, {"emoji": "⁉️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "Gdoll_evil", "emoji_id": "1513274391801106472", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🫃", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "❤️‍🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "Ryker_pray", "emoji_id": "1468258632205340820", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "💦", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1518527531299508325", "filename": "CN.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3634534, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1518527530737467533/1518527531299508325/CN.png?ex=6a3ae738&is=6a3995b8&hm=4d339d89600c8b543b220ea8fd184dc4c1bef12672ea308793250d9fe5726a8c&"}, {"id": "1518527532041765115", "filename": "EN.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3610480, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1